{{vgname2|向日葵互动娱乐软件|en=Sunflowers Interactive Entertainment Software}}，是[[德国|德国]]一家游戏开发和发布公司。该公司由公司总裁阿迪·博伊科和首席执行官Wilhelm Hamrozi创建于1993年，总部设立在德国[[霍伊森斯塔姆|霍伊森斯塔姆]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mcvuk.com/development/ubisoft-snaps-up-sunflowers|title=Ubisoft snaps up SunFlowers|last=FRENCH|first=MICHAEL|date=2007-04-11|website=mcvuk.com|accessdate=2018-07-18|language=en|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180823061943/https://www.mcvuk.com/development/ubisoft-snaps-up-sunflowers|archivedate=2018-08-23}}</ref>。

2007年4月11日，[[育碧|育碧]]宣布已收购了向日葵娱乐互动软件<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/104435/Ubisoft_Acquires_SunFlowers_Anno_Franchise.php |title=Ubisoft Acquires SunFlowers,  Anno  Franchise |first=Brandon |last=Boyer |date=2007-04-11 |website=gamasutra.com |accessdate=2018-07-18 |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180823062041/https://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/104435/Ubisoft_Acquires_SunFlowers_Anno_Franchise.php |archivedate=2018-08-23 }}</ref>。

